出嚟鳩噏</blockquote>晒氣啦，班仆街到時咪屌梁游只網上呼籲，唔落街拉票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似毓民上次屌梁天琦只在網上呼籲投鄭錦滿，唔落街拉票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毓民同長毛而家仲有人信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64de6fc8a7a49fb01d22c0d798752ae912396f1c","tid":960694,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"個標題都誤導既<br />\n梁頌恆都唔係話要投票支持長毛<br />\n佢話長毛有權參選「拿回」佢一席<br />\n至於D人補選時投唔投長毛, WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以最好都係唔好接受毒果訪問, 出到黎既野會係被扭曲"},{"pid":"62ad7de2b1ee394203885d563117c7b5267f14a9","tid":960694,"uid":12798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"擺長毛上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e7e6dbce229c304903ab22e0b41e404c91168a","tid":960694,"uid":8577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"巴治奧明玩𨳊佢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好講長毛個朵咁臭飯民狗都未必投佢，就算派個大佬出嚟都未必選得贏保皇狗啦"},{"pid":"e4a0fb11c6a10037bc1f70251dd428e5386e974f","tid":960694,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca39c924c040f2b651cb0d239012c73f59084f2e","tid":960694,"uid":223741,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"個位本身係佢<br />\n比政府政治審判DQ咁正常係佢補選㗎<br />\n我支持佢繼續屌票喎<br />\n繼續以身作則唔好退縮啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iDc3sw2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiDc3sw2.png&h=d78c60f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持長毛繼續屌票<br />\n咁都有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc5a11882995b82204dbbbe69d4a25