g><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肥共黎至叻有事鍾無艷，冇事Dup你春！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇毛共諜輸鳩左又屌票又loop過！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之都係個句，扮民尤其大愛支都係共諜，不過係同京劇班主下既裝黑臉，同白紅臉一齊戲至襟睇，旨在燒港豬時間意志幫共狗奪取更多空間權力！！！</span></span></span></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1217b7825c7ee97b9196d8a0b93a27f358c030c","tid":960694,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382bb4b265147c06039d9f6e5ab2d381dc959720","tid":960694,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e822978523e0faca1a4af19c176698fcdcda4","tid":960694,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b9fd3e27dfa94aa28b956f336ced8816d426d","tid":960694,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63c7ae32541e149c3817304697f02ff148422c36","tid":960694,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"暗黑兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"估下 梁頌恆endorse 吸既本土票多D<br />\n定 長毛出選 屌走既本土票多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}